        {
          "scid": "sn35.67:1.1",
          "pli": "“‘Dukkhaṃ, dukkhan’ti, bhante, vuccati. ",
          "en": "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘suffering’. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.67:1.2",
          "pli": "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, dukkhaṃ vā assa dukkhapaññatti vā”ti … pe …. ",
          "en": "How do we define suffering or what is known as suffering?” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.67:1.3",
          "pli": "Pañcamaṃ. ",
